snippet.title: Concept Destruction - Xbox One Gameplay
snippet.description:
If you took Destruction Derby or Wreckfest and made tiny cars out of cardboard, Concept Destruction is the result. Not too bad of a game from a smaller developer like that.

Concept Destruction (C) ThinIce
Published by Ratalaika Games
Also available on Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Nintendo Switch and Steam
